data.description: Come get your slice of country heaven with this great house in Loma, CO. This ranch style layout has Four bedrooms, Three bathrooms with over 2,000 Square Feet and over a half-acre lot. Room to spare inside and out! RV parking and a great yard to enjoy year-round. House comes with Owned Solar Panels to help keep your energy bills low. Set up your showing today.
